{"tid":1666784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日係連登五毛開放日？","createTime":"2019-10-21T06:30:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T08:01:42.000Z","uid":61886,"like":7,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c7ba2cf6639745e7f1ca2a323aa00f7218bc71bf","tid":1666784,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:30:05.000Z","msg":"個個post都一班人搵交嗌<br />\n好聲好氣講唔得架咩<br />\n句句都串柒柒<br />\n講野又無point<br />\n討論無論點<br />\n一味互屌<br />\n依啲係咪自己人自己諗下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9q341K9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9q341K9.png&h=f0b142d3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QMcJxRS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQMcJxRS.png&h=613ec0d2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v7jG3Yy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv7jG3Yy.png&h=93b863ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n任何人提出意見或建議都係對抗爭好<br />\n提出意見唔使講有無資格<br />\n有point有論點就得<br />\n無手足係100%岩晒<br />\n大家互相補鑊 互相包容 互相理解<br />\nbe humble 連對手足都做唔到<br />\n好快比啲五毛搞散<br />\n<br />\nbtw 我就算出行動post都有五毛撞入黎串柒柒<br />\n不過通常五毛講野都無point<br />\n剩係識搵交嗌"},{"pid":"ace6039f8b670a0d71057d221f8adc3a29ff8abb","tid":1666784,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:30:16.000Z","msg":"不如全港黨鐵靜坐聲討721啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665580</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16ff71bd90ed0a10ec3b496b9fe729836b2accc2","tid":1666784,"uid":176282,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:30:56.000Z","msg":"日日都係"},{"pid":"6c76673f12fd6cf8c6fe4a8ba8ab86e4e8d55e69","tid":1666784,"uid":288670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T06:32:24.000Z","msg":"清真寺加721 三個月 一定要搵野轉移焦點"},{"pid":"a0114eb334dc5496b46ece1862be9abdac14d497",